Games.Title: Left 4 Dead 2
Games.Description: Set in the zombie apocalypse, Left 4 Dead 2 (L4D2) is the highly anticipated sequel to the award-winning Left 4 Dead, the #1 co-op game of 2008. This co-operative action horror FPS takes you and your friends through the cities, swamps and cemeteries of the Deep South, from Savannah to New Orleans across five expansive campaigns.

Games.Title: Counter-Strike: Global Offensive
Games.Description: Counter-Strike: Global Offensive (CS: GO) will expand upon the team-based action gameplay that it pioneered when it was launched 14 years ago. CS: GO features new maps, characters, and weapons and delivers updated versions of the classic CS content (de_dust2, etc.).

Games.Title: OpenRA (Red Alert)
Games.Description: Classic strategy games, rebuilt for the modern era. Open Source. Free. For all modern operating systems.
